<paragraph blockId="20.[151,1437,258,1978]" pageId="20" pageNumber="321">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,1449,1474]" pageId="20" pageNumber="321">Etymology.</emphasis>
We are pleased to name this species after Sueli Pereira, a mayfly specialist who kindly provided material treated in this work.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
